---
class: dark, middle, center
# Modelo por sección

---
class: regular

# `group_nest()`

```{r}
mtcars %>%
  group_nest(cyl)
```

---
class: regular

# `map()`

```{r}
mtcars %>%
  group_nest(cyl) %>%
  mutate(modelos = map(data, ~lm(mpg ~ wt, data = .x)))
```

---
class: regular
# `map()` + `unnest()` 

```{r}
mtcars %>%
  group_nest(cyl) %>%
  mutate(modelos = map(data, ~lm(mpg ~ wt, data = .x)),
         resultados = map(modelos, glance)) %>%
  unnest(resultados)
```

